Package: dsVertClient
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Client Functions for Vertically Partitioned Data
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Sarrat González", email = "david.sarrat@isglobal.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Miron", "Banjac", email = "miron.banjac@isglobal.org",
           role = "aut"),
    person("Juan R", "González", email = "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org",
           role = "aut")
  )
Description: Client-side DataSHIELD functions for privacy-preserving analysis
    of vertically partitioned federated data. Provides user-facing functions
    for record alignment, correlation analysis via Multiparty Homomorphic
    Encryption (MHE) with threshold decryption, PCA, and Generalized Linear
    Models across multiple data sources. Works with the companion dsVert
    server package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/isglobal-brge/dsVertClient,
    https://isglobal-brge.github.io/dsVertClient/
BugReports: https://github.com/isglobal-brge/dsVertClient/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
